          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main>

      <FeaturesGeneral
        title="Meeting Your Travel and Event Expectations"
        subTitle="At PKT Travels, we understand the complexities of planning unforgettable journeys and seamless events. Whether you're exploring new destinations or hosting a grand celebration, our team is dedicated to making every moment exceptional, ensuring your experience exceeds expectations."

        features={features}
      />

      <FeaturesNavs
        title=`Customize <span class="text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400">PKT TRAVELS, TOURS & EVENTS</span>'s offerings to perfectly suit your Travel & Event needs.`
        tabs={[
          {
            heading: "Dedicated Event & Travel Planning Teams",
            content:
              "Benefit from our dedicated and experienced teams who ensure every aspect of your travel or event is managed with precision and care. From booking the perfect itinerary to handling every detail of your event, our experts provide personalized support every step of the way.",
