            src: tools,
            alt: "Yellow and black heavy equipment on brown grass field",
            first: true,
          },
          {
            heading: "Effortless, Cost-Effective Travel & Event Experiences",
            content:
              "Discover affordable and stress-free solutions with PKT Travels, Tours & Events. We streamline your booking process, making both travel and event planning more efficient, all while keeping it within your budget. Enjoy amazing experiences without the hassle.",
            svg: "dashboard",
            src: dashboard,
            alt: "A screenshot or graphic representation of the intuitive dashboard",
            second: true,
          },
          {
            heading: "Customized Travel & Event Solutions for Every Need",
            content:
              "At PKT Travels, Tours & Events, we offer personalized travel and event packages tailored to your unique preferences and goals. Whether it's an adventurous tour, a corporate retreat, or a destination wedding, we work closely with you to design experiences that reflect your vision and exceed expectations.",
            svg: "house",
            src: construction,
            alt: "Gray metal building frame near tower crane during daytime",
          },
        ]}
      />

      <TestimonialsSection
        title="Why Choose PKT Travels, Tours & Events?"
        subTitle="With PKT Travels, you don’t just get a travel agency or event planner—you get a trusted partner who’s always one step ahead. Our innovative tools, personalized service, and years of expertise ensure that your trip or event will be executed smoothly and efficiently, every time. From real-time updates on travel to seamless event coordination, we take care of the details so you can focus on the experience."
        ;
        testimonials={[
          {
            content:
              "PKT Travels completely transformed how we manage our company retreats and special events. Their quick response times and exceptional attention to detail helped us meet even the tightest deadlines without compromising on quality. Our team now relies on them for flawless, Visa processing, Ticket booking, travel and event management!",
            author: "Michael Mensah",
            role: "Logistics Director | GlobalTrade Solutions Inc.",
            avatarSrc:
              "https://res.cloudinary.com/dzh8mryxw/image/upload/v1734371171/kaysha-OJvh3njqTTQ-unsplash_od6pkn.jpg",
          },
        ]}
        statistics={[
          {
            count: "70k+",
            description:
              "events flawlessly executed across the globe—from intimate corporate retreats to large-scale international conferences.",
          },
          {
            count: "90%",
            description:
              "we have a proud 90% Visa Success Record",
          },
          {
            count: "25.3%",
            description:
              "reduction in overall travel expenses thanks to PKT Travels' exclusive partnerships and cost-effective travel solutions.",
          },
          {
            count: "3x",
            description: "faster planning and booking for both travel and events with our efficient, user-friendly booking platform and real-time updates.",
          },
        ]}
      />

      <PricingSection pricing={pricing} />

      <FAQ title="Frequently<br />asked questions" faqs={faqs} />

      
    </main>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<script define:vars={{ backgroundImages }}>
  const backgrounds = backgroundImages.map(img => img.src);
  
  let currentIndex = 0;
  const slideshowElement = document.getElementById('slideshowBackground');

  function changeBackground() {
    currentIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % backgrounds.length;
    if (slideshowElement) {
      slideshowElement.style.backgroundImage = `url('${backgrounds[currentIndex]}')`;
    }
  }

  setInterval(changeBackground, 10000);
</script>
